016package org.lifstools.jgoslin.parser;
017
018import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.LipidMolecularSpecies;
019import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.ConstraintViolationException;
020import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.LipidStructureDefined;
021import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.LipidFaBondType;
022import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.LipidClassMeta;
023import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.LipidSnPosition;
024import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.Headgroup;
025import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.LipidClasses;
026import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.LipidCompleteStructure;
027import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.LipidAdduct;
028import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.Adduct;
029import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.LipidLevel;
030import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.LipidCategory;
031import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.FattyAcid;
032import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.LipidSpecies;
033import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.LipidFullStructure;
034import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.HeadgroupDecorator;
035import java.util.ArrayList;
036import java.util.Arrays;
037import java.util.HashSet;
038import java.util.LinkedList;
039import java.util.List;
040import java.util.Map;
041import static java.util.Map.entry;
042import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.Element;
043import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.FunctionalGroup;
044import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.KnownFunctionalGroups;
045import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.LipidParsingException;
046
047/**
048 *
049 * @author Dominik Kopczynski
050 * @author Nils Hoffmann
051 */
052public abstract class LipidBaseParserEventHandler extends BaseParserEventHandler<LipidAdduct> {
053
054    protected LipidLevel level = LipidLevel.COMPLETE_STRUCTURE;
055    protected String headGroup = "";
056    protected FattyAcid lcb = null;
057    protected List<FattyAcid> faList = new LinkedList<>();
058    protected FattyAcid currentFa = null;
059    protected Adduct adduct = null;
060    protected ArrayList<HeadgroupDecorator> headgroupDecorators = new ArrayList<>();
061    protected boolean useHeadGroup = false;
062    protected KnownFunctionalGroups knownFunctionalGroups;
063    
064    private static final Map<String, ArrayList<String>> GLYCO_TABLE = Map.ofEntries(
065        entry("ga2", new ArrayList<String>(Arrays.asList("GalNAc", "Gal", "Glc"))),
066        entry("gb3", new ArrayList<String>(Arrays.asList("Gal", "Gal", "Glc"))),
067        entry("gb4", new ArrayList<String>(Arrays.asList("GalNAc", "Gal", "Gal", "Glc"))),
068        entry("gd1", new ArrayList<String>(Arrays.asList("Gal", "GalNAc", "NeuAc", "NeuAc", "Gal", "Glc"))),
069        entry("gd1a", new ArrayList<String>(Arrays.asList("Hex", "Hex", "Hex", "HexNAc", "NeuAc", "NeuAc"))),
070        entry("gd2", new ArrayList<String>(Arrays.asList("GalNAc", "NeuAc", "NeuAc", "Gal", "Glc"))),
071        entry("gd3", new ArrayList<String>(Arrays.asList("NeuAc", "NeuAc", "Gal", "Glc"))),
072        entry("gm1", new ArrayList<String>(Arrays.asList("Gal", "GalNAc", "NeuAc", "Gal", "Glc"))),
073        entry("gm2", new ArrayList<String>(Arrays.asList("GalNAc", "NeuAc", "Gal", "Glc"))),
074        entry("gm3", new ArrayList<String>(Arrays.asList("NeuAc", "Gal", "Glc"))),
075        entry("gm4", new ArrayList<String>(Arrays.asList("NeuAc", "Gal"))),
076        entry("gp1", new ArrayList<String>(Arrays.asList("NeuAc", "NeuAc", "Gal", "GalNAc", "NeuAc", "NeuAc", "NeuAc", "Gal", "Glc"))),
077        entry("gq1", new ArrayList<String>(Arrays.asList("NeuAc", "Gal", "GalNAc", "NeuAc", "NeuAc", "NeuAc", "Gal", "Glc"))),
078        entry("gt1", new ArrayList<String>(Arrays.asList("Gal", "GalNAc", "NeuAc", "NeuAc", "NeuAc", "Gal", "Glc"))),
079        entry("gt2", new ArrayList<String>(Arrays.asList("GalNAc", "NeuAc", "NeuAc", "NeuAc", "Gal", "Glc"))),
080        entry("gt3", new ArrayList<String>(Arrays.asList("NeuAc", "NeuAc", "NeuAc", "Gal", "Glc")))
081    );
082
083    protected static HashSet<String> SP_EXCEPTION_CLASSES = new HashSet<>(Arrays.asList("Cer", "Ceramide", "Sphingosine", "So", "Sphinganine", "Sa", "SPH", "Sph", "LCB"));
084
085    public LipidBaseParserEventHandler(KnownFunctionalGroups knownFunctionalGroups) {
086        this.knownFunctionalGroups = knownFunctionalGroups;
087    }
088
089    protected void setLipidLevel(LipidLevel _level) {
090        level = level.level < _level.level ? level : _level;
091    }
092
093    protected boolean spRegularLcb() {
094        return Headgroup.getCategory(headGroup) == LipidCategory.SP && (currentFa.getLipidFaBondType() == LipidFaBondType.LCB_REGULAR || currentFa.getLipidFaBondType() == LipidFaBondType.LCB_EXCEPTION) && !(SP_EXCEPTION_CLASSES.contains(headGroup) && headgroupDecorators.isEmpty());
095    }
096
097    protected Headgroup prepareHeadgroupAndChecks() {
098        
099        String hg = headGroup.toLowerCase();
100        if (GLYCO_TABLE.containsKey(hg)){
101            for (String carbohydrate : GLYCO_TABLE.get(hg)){
102                FunctionalGroup functional_group = null;
103                try {
104                    functional_group = knownFunctionalGroups.get(carbohydrate);
105                } catch (Exception e) {
106                    throw new LipidParsingException("Carbohydrate '" + carbohydrate + "' unknown");
107                }
108
109                functional_group.getElements().put(Element.O, functional_group.getElements().get(Element.O) - 1);
110                headgroupDecorators.add((HeadgroupDecorator) functional_group);
111
112            }
113            headGroup = "Cer";
114        }
115        
116        
117        Headgroup headgroup = new Headgroup(headGroup, headgroupDecorators, useHeadGroup);
118        if (useHeadGroup) {
119            return headgroup;
120        }
121        
122        headGroup = headgroup.getClassName();
123
124        int true_fa = 0;
125        for (FattyAcid fa : faList) {
126            true_fa += (fa.getNumCarbon() > 0 || fa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() > 0) ? 1 : 0;
127        }
128        int poss_fa = (LipidClasses.getInstance().size() > headgroup.getLipidClass()) ? LipidClasses.getInstance().get(headgroup.getLipidClass()).possibleNumFa : 0;
129
130        // make lyso
131        boolean can_be_lyso = (LipidClasses.getInstance().size() > Headgroup.getClass("L" + headGroup)) ? LipidClasses.getInstance().get(Headgroup.getClass("L" + headGroup)).specialCases.contains("Lyso") : false;
132        LipidClassMeta l = LipidClasses.getInstance().get(Headgroup.getClass("LCL"));
133        if ((true_fa + 1 == poss_fa || true_fa + 2 == poss_fa) && level != LipidLevel.SPECIES && headgroup.getLipidCategory() == LipidCategory.GP && can_be_lyso) {
134            if (true_fa + 1 == poss_fa) headGroup = "L" + headGroup;
135            else headGroup = "DL" + headGroup;
136            headgroup = new Headgroup(headGroup, headgroupDecorators, useHeadGroup);
137            poss_fa = (LipidClasses.getInstance().size() > headgroup.getLipidClass()) ? LipidClasses.getInstance().get(headgroup.getLipidClass()).possibleNumFa : 0;
138        }
139        
140        else if ((true_fa + 1 == poss_fa || true_fa + 2 == poss_fa) && level != LipidLevel.SPECIES && headgroup.getLipidCategory() == LipidCategory.GL && headGroup.equals("TG")) {
141            if (true_fa + 1 == poss_fa) headGroup = "DG";
142            else headGroup = "MG";
143            headgroup = new Headgroup(headGroup, headgroupDecorators, useHeadGroup);
144            poss_fa = (LipidClasses.getInstance().size() > headgroup.getLipidClass()) ? LipidClasses.getInstance().get(headgroup.getLipidClass()).possibleNumFa : 0;
145        }
146        
147
148        if (level == LipidLevel.SPECIES) {
149            if (true_fa == 0 && poss_fa != 0) {
150                throw new ConstraintViolationException("No fatty acyl information lipid class '" + headgroup.getHeadgroup() + "' provided.");
151            }
152        } else if (true_fa != poss_fa && LipidLevel.isLevel(level, LipidLevel.COMPLETE_STRUCTURE.level | LipidLevel.FULL_STRUCTURE.level | LipidLevel.STRUCTURE_DEFINED.level)) {
153            throw new ConstraintViolationException("Number of described fatty acyl chains (" + Integer.toString(true_fa) + ") not allowed for lipid class '" + headgroup.getHeadgroup() + "' (having " + Integer.toString(poss_fa) + " fatty aycl chains).");
154        } else if (LipidClasses.getInstance().get(Headgroup.getClass(headGroup)).specialCases.contains("Lyso") && true_fa > poss_fa){
155            throw new ConstraintViolationException("Number of described fatty acyl chains (" + Integer.toString(true_fa) + ") not allowed for lipid class '" + headgroup.getHeadgroup() + "' (having " + Integer.toString(poss_fa) + " fatty aycl chains).");
156        }
157
158        if (LipidClasses.getInstance().get(headgroup.getLipidClass()).specialCases.contains("HC")) {
159            faList.get(0).setLipidFaBondType(LipidFaBondType.ETHER);
160        }
161
162        if (LipidClasses.getInstance().get(headgroup.getLipidClass()).specialCases.contains("Amide")) {
163            for (FattyAcid fatty : faList){
164                fatty.setLipidFaBondType(LipidFaBondType.AMIDE);
165            }
166        }
167
168        int max_num_fa = (LipidClasses.getInstance().size() > headgroup.getLipidClass()) ? LipidClasses.getInstance().get(headgroup.getLipidClass()).maxNumFa : 0;
169        if (max_num_fa != faList.size()) {
170            setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.MOLECULAR_SPECIES);
171        }
172
173        if (faList.size() > 0 && headgroup.isSpException()) {
174            faList.get(0).setType(LipidFaBondType.LCB_EXCEPTION);
175        }
176
177        return headgroup;
178    }
179
180    protected LipidSpecies assembleLipid(Headgroup headgroup) {
181        for (FattyAcid fa : faList){
182            if (fa.stereoInformationMissing()){
183                setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.FULL_STRUCTURE);
184                break;
185            }
186        }
187        
188        LipidSpecies ls = null;
189        switch (level) {
190            case COMPLETE_STRUCTURE ->
191                ls = new LipidCompleteStructure(headgroup, faList, knownFunctionalGroups);
192            case FULL_STRUCTURE ->
193                ls = new LipidFullStructure(headgroup, faList, knownFunctionalGroups);
194            case STRUCTURE_DEFINED ->
195                ls = new LipidStructureDefined(headgroup, faList, knownFunctionalGroups);
196            case SN_POSITION ->
197                ls = new LipidSnPosition(headgroup, faList, knownFunctionalGroups);
198            case MOLECULAR_SPECIES ->
199                ls = new LipidMolecularSpecies(headgroup, faList, knownFunctionalGroups);
200            case SPECIES ->
201                ls = new LipidSpecies(headgroup, faList, knownFunctionalGroups);
202            default -> {
203            }
204        }
205        return ls;
206    }
207
208}
